The '''''Klivering''''' was a smuggling vessel used by [[Ellor]]. It was part of the [[Smugglers' Alliance]] fleet in the [[Battle of Bilbringi (9 ABY)|Battle of Bilbringi]], running flanking position to the ''[[Kai Mir]]'' when they entered the [[Bilbringi Shipyards|shipyards]].

